<refsect1 xml:id='description'><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para><function>Tk_SetCaretPos</function> sets the caret location for the display of the
specified Tk_Window <emphasis remap='I'>tkwin</emphasis>.  The caret is the per-display cursor
location used for indicating global focus (e.g. to comply with Microsoft
Accessibility guidelines), as well as for location of the over-the-spot XIM
(X Input Methods) or Windows IME windows.</para>

</refsect1>

